 addUserKnob {20 info_tab l INFO}
 addUserKnob {26 info_text l "" +STARTLINE T "Tool made @ Illogic studios.\n\nTracking Glints/Flare by using PRef/Rest and depth Pass, useful for Swarovski productions.\n\nLogs :\nVersion 0.1 \[14/01/2026] : First Release\nVersion 0.2 \[20/01/2026] : Fixed bad Scale computing / Fixed Edge Selection on PRef / Added Rotation Animation settings\nVersion 0.3 \[21/01/2026] : Added Gain Animation settings\nVersion 0.4 \[22/01/2026] : Better UI\nVersion 0.5 \[25/03/2026] : Better position sampling / added selection mask input /removed backgrond and matte input / changed sine wave anim to noise wave anim"}
 addUserKnob {1 nametag +INVISIBLE}
 nametag ILGC_OFTracker
