   ypos 399
   addUserKnob {20 User}
   addUserKnob {4 shapeTypesPDC l Type M {Sphere "Sphere (2 Points)" "Sphere (Hollow)" "Cube (Rounded)" "Cube (Sharp)" Torus Cylinder Cone Octahedron Dome Pyramid Ramp "" "" "" "" "" "" "" "" "" "" "" "" "" "" ""}}
